The `{ }` is supposed to declare a dictionary, using a [flow collection syntax][1]

You seem to declare two dictionaries, each with the same key &quot;`name`&quot;

Check if the content if  `{{ pdt_type }}.yml` is actually the issue, by using a simpler content:

